Author: budqueen12
Text: Oh my god me. I literally have days where I'm like, you know what. Weight gain is fine! I'm not even fat! Listen to your body! Eat what you want! And I'll hardly track and eat probably over maintenance and be fine with it. Makes me feel like I'm recovered and fine. Other days I'll feel the absolute need to starve myself and eat like an unexpected almond or something and freak out and run to try purge it. Like. ?????
